      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs Seewas Odijas\nBehrni / Nakama Mahjas ta\nTehwa Kegila bija : Garmi un\nEstemoa tas Mäekattiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Gihmaxa Behrnibi-\nja: Ammons un Rinnus / Be-\nnanans un Tifons. Un Jeseüts\nBehrni bija Soëts/ un Ben-\nSoëts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Seelus Juhda Deb-\nla / Behrni bija : Gers Leka\nTehws / un Laëdus Maresa\nTehws/ un to Wehwernu Raddi\nfemin Asvea Namimu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Joküns un tee Wibri\nno Kosebas / un Joas/ un Sa-\nraws/ kas pahr teem Moabite-\nreem waldischi/ un Jasubi La-\neimâ/ bet tahs Leetas jaw irr\nwezzas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee bija Pohdneeki / un\ntinnahs ar Dehstischanas un\nSehtu Darrischanas pee ta Keh-\nnixa Darbeem/ tur tee palikke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gihmeana Behrnu Raddu Raffti : 24. Un to\npaschu Uswarreschanu prett teem Amalekite-\nreem : 43\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gihmeana Behrni bi-\nja: Nemuels un Ja-\nwins / un Jaribs/\nSeerus/ Sauls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Dehls bija Sallums/\nta Dehls bija Mibsaïms/ta Dehls\nbija Misinus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mismus Behrni bi-\nja Annuels/ ta Dehls bija Sa-\nkurs/ ta Dehls bija Simejus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Simejum bija feſch-\npadesmitsDehlu/un feſchas Met-\ntas/ bet winna Brahteem ne bi-\nja dauds Behrnu. Un wiſſi\nwinnu Raddi ne wairojahs tik\ndauds/ ka tee Behrni Juhda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee dſihwoja eeſſich\nBerſebas/ un Moladas un Azar\nSuata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un eeſſich Bilas/ un E-\nzemä un Tolada.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Betuelä / un Ormä/\nun Ziklagä.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un BetMarkabotä / un\nAzarsustina/ un Betbiërä / un\nSaraïma. Schee bija winnu\nPilsfahti/ teekams Dahwids par\nKehniku tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnu Zeemi bija E-\ntang un Ains / Riminons un\nTokens/ un Asans/ pezi Pils-\nfahti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſi winnu Zeemi/\nkas apkahrt fcheem Pilsfahteem\nbija lihds Bäälam/ fchi irr win-\nnu Dſihwofchana un winnu\nRaddu-Raksti winnu Starpä.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mesobabs/ un Jam-\nleks/ un Josus Amaztjus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Joëls / un Jeüs Jo-\nsuja Dehls/ ta Dehla Seraja/\nAsiëta Dehla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Elioënajus/un Jaëko-\nbus/un Jesoajus/ un Asajus/ un\nAdtets/ un Jesimeels/ un Be-\nnajus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sisus/ Siweja Dehls\nFFFF ta\n"
